room_title: Escape room "Quest of Honor" by Exit Strategy in Charlotte

room_description: A gold hungry dragon is laying fire to the medieval town of Westwend. The castle's only hope lays with your small band of heroes. Can you figure out how to defeat the great dragon and retrieve the long lost artifact it had been protecting?
